        "title": "fix(feishu): add pagination support for drive list and info",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nFeishu drive list/info missing pagination support\n\n## Changes\n\n- `extensions/feishu/src/drive-schema.ts`: Add page_size, page_token, and all parameters\n- `extensions/feishu/src/drive.ts`: Add pagination loop with MAX_LIST_PAGES cap (100)\n- `extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-drive/SKILL.md`: Document pagination parameters for list action\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n**Behavior addressed**: Feishu drive list and info actions now support pagination via page_size, page_token, and all parameters.\n\n**Evidence after fix**:\n\n```text\n$ npx tsx -e '...'\nPagination params verified in FeishuDriveSchema: page_size ✅ page_token ✅ all ✅\n\n$ node scripts/test-projects.mjs extensions/feishu/src/drive.test.ts\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  19 passed (19)\n```\n\nPagination bounded at 100 pages (MAX_LIST_PAGES). When `all: true` the loop continues via has_more + page_token until exhausted or capped.\n\n**What was not tested**: End-to-end with a real Feishu tenant >10 items.\n\nCloses: #93928",
